      "content": "it just feels like a lie. that \"path forward\" stuff... it's just something people say to feel better, but it doesn't change the reality. the debt is real. the loss is real. the way everyone is going to look at me is real. i feel like i'm just waiting for the floor to fall out from under me completely. i'm just so tired of fighting a battle that was lost months ago.",
